Introduction

Anthonny is a Filipino-Japanese trainee signed with YY Entertainment.

He gained fame as a participant in the Korean reality show “Boys Planet” and the Japanese competition show “Produce 101 Japan Season 2”.

Anthonny is a member of the J-POP group TOZ, under YY Entertainment. They made their debut on September 27, 2023 with the mini album FLARE.
